<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>161</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Damlai tuipi chunga ka vaih,
 Lai hin aw, ka Lal Isu;
 Ka luchung zawna vakin,
 Ka masang lam salhvak in;
 Huih a nungin van a nim,
 Lungkham tuipi a kinawk.

[V2]
 Thim a hung khawk tieng ka vai,
 Lungkham a kinawk, ka kap;
 Hetloh gam ka tawh laiin,
 Ka keng vengin Lal Isu
 Ka masangah chieh in la,
 Na khut in ei tu zingin.

[V3]
 2. Sun leh zan um lo thei ei puoi,
 Damlai tuipi chung ahin;
 Himahleh ka Lal Isu;
 Thimnan Na mel a lieh tieng,
 Thavai in kei ka mau a,
 Nanga din vang a thim puoi.

[V4]
 3. Thieng leh thienglo kikal ahin,
 Munsang leh munniem ahin,
 Chieh ding dan ka hethiem puoi,
 Nangin chieh dan ei hilhin,
 Mun nuom leh mun haksa ah.
 Na khutin ei tu zingin.

[V5]
 4. Aw thawk laia mauna haw hi,
 Hehpihna I ti thei dem?
 Himahleh van lopi na,
 A bukima I chan tieng,
 Damsung haksa chawm cha hi,
 Genkham in I ngai zel dem?</lyrics>
<title>Ka Keng Vengin Lal Isu</title>
</song>